<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I think it is usefull get the timezone by the locale region or by the default region of a given language
e.g:
de_DE =&gt; DE =&gt; Europe/Berlin
de_AT =&gt; AT   =&gt; Europe/Vienna
en        =&gt; GB  =&gt; Europe/London       (using the default region or throw an Exception)</p>

<p>the information is stored in the file Zend/Locale/Data/supplementalData.xml</p>

    </div>
